this behavior is puzzling. 

``` python
def leaves(self, root=None):
        """Get leaves of the whole tree of a subtree."""
        leaves = []
        if root is None:
            for node in self._nodes.values():
                if node.is_leaf():
                    leaves.append(node)
        else:
            for node in self.expand_tree(root):
                if self[node].is_leaf():
                    leaves.append(node)
